---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Base
  title="Body by Olga — Strength After 40"
  description="Body by Olga — strength training, food awareness, and consistency coaching for women 40+ who are done starting over. 30-minute home workouts. Start your free trial."
>
  <Nav />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="hero-g">
        <div>
          <p class="hero-ey r">Strength After 40</p>
          <h1 class="r d1">Stop getting weaker.<br><em>Start here.</em></h1>
          <p class="hero-sub r d2">You've solved harder problems than this. 30-minute home workouts, food awareness, and coaching support for women 40+ who are done starting over.</p>
          <div class="hero-a r d3">
            <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-p">Start Your 7-Day Free Trial <svg class="arr" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
            <a href="#method" class="btn btn-s">See how it works</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="r d2">
          <div class="hero-img">
            <img src="/images/hero-image.png" alt="Olga training with dumbbells" loading="eager" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOCIAL PROOF (HIDDEN) -->
  <!-- <section class="proof r">
    <div class="ctn">
      <p class="proof-l">Featured In</p>
      <div class="proof-r">
        <span>Self</span><span>Vogue</span><span>Cosmopolitan</span><span>New York Post</span><span>USA Today</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section> -->

  <!-- RECOGNITION FLIP CARDS -->
  <section class="recog sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="recog-h r">
        <h2>You know what to do. You just can't make it stick.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="recog-g">

        <div class="flip-card recog-flip r">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front recog-front">
              <p>You've managed a career, a family, and more responsibility than most people can imagine.</p>
              <p>But your body feels like the one area where you keep losing ground. You start strong. Then stress hits, the week falls apart, and you're back to square one.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-recog-1.png" alt="Olga" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>You're not starting over. You're starting right.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card recog-flip r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front recog-front">
              <p>You've tried the diets. The apps. The "just be more disciplined" approach.</p>
              <p>It works for a few weeks. Then the all-or-nothing cycle kicks in and you quit — not because you're lazy, but because the system was never built for your actual life.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-recog-2.png" alt="Olga with food" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Food is not the enemy.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card recog-flip r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front recog-front">
              <p class="em">What if the problem was never willpower?</p>
              <p class="em">What if the real issue is the patterns behind the habits — the stress eating, the all-or-nothing thinking, the shame that makes consistency harder?</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-recog-3.png" alt="Olga thinking" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>It's the patterns, not you.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section class="philo sp" id="philosophy">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="philo-in r">
        <h2>This is not another plan.<br>It's a different way of <em>thinking.</em></h2>
        <div class="philo-cols">
          <div class="philo-col">
            <h3>What we believe</h3>
            <p>Behavior change beats motivation. Systems last. Motivation fades.</p>
            <p>Exercise is not punishment. Training is for strength, energy, and confidence — not to earn food.</p>
            <p>Consistency matters more than perfection. A hard week needs adjustments, not quitting. Plan B still counts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="philo-col">
            <h3>What we do differently</h3>
            <p>We don't just hand you workouts. We help you understand why you do what you do — the emotional eating patterns, the self-sabotage, the all-or-nothing cycle.</p>
            <p>We teach food awareness, not rigid dieting. Hunger is data. Fullness matters. Awareness beats rules.</p>
            <p>This program is built to make healthy habits feel natural again.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE METHOD FLIP CARDS -->
  <section class="sp" id="method">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="system-h r">
        <h2>The Method</h2>
        <p>Four pillars. One system. Built for real life.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="system-g">

        <div class="flip-card method-flip r">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">Pillar 01</div>
              <h3>Functional Strength</h3>
              <p>Daily 30-minute dumbbell workouts designed for women 40+. Short, effective, progressive. Train at home in the time you actually have.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-1.png" alt="Olga training" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Functional Strength</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card method-flip r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">Pillar 02</div>
              <h3>Food Awareness</h3>
              <p>No rigid meal plans. Learn to recognize hunger, understand emotional eating patterns, and build food skills that work in real life.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-2.png" alt="Olga with food" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Food Awareness</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card method-flip r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">Pillar 03</div>
              <h3>Mindset & Behavior</h3>
              <p>Address the patterns that keep you stuck — perfectionism, shame, all-or-nothing thinking, and the cycle of starting over every Monday.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-3.png" alt="Olga mindset" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Mindset & Behavior</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card method-flip r d3">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">Pillar 04</div>
              <h3>Consistency System</h3>
              <p>Streaks, community, daily structure, and coaching-backed support that makes showing up feel like identity — not willpower.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-4.png" alt="Olga consistency" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Consistency System</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INSIDE THE APP FLIP CARDS -->
  <section class="app-s sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="app-h r">
        <h2>Inside the App</h2>
        <p>Everything you need to train, eat with awareness, and stay consistent — in one place.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-g">

        <div class="flip-card app-flip r">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i o"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
              <h4>Follow-Along Workouts</h4>
              <p>30-minute strength sessions. Press play and train with Olga.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-2.png" alt="Workout screen" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card app-flip r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i t"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12h8"/><path d="M12 8v8"/></svg></div>
              <h4>Dumbbell-Only Programs</h4>
              <p>No gym needed. Train at home with a few pairs of dumbbells.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-1.png" alt="App home" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card app-flip r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i o"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Z"/><path d="M12 14a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4Z"/></svg></div>
              <h4>Nutrition Guidance</h4>
              <p>Food awareness tools, hunger skills, and meal structure — not calorie obsession.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-6.png" alt="Nutrition tracking" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card app-flip r">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i t"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg></div>
              <h4>Mindset Coaching</h4>
              <p>Daily prompts that address behavior, emotional eating, and self-sabotage patterns.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-3.png" alt="Calendar" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card app-flip r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i o"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
              <h4>Streaks & Progress</h4>
              <p>Track workouts, build streaks, and see real evidence that you're getting stronger.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-4.png" alt="Streaks" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flip-card app-flip r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i t"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
              <h4>Community</h4>
              <p>Women 40+ building strength together. Support, accountability, and shared wins.</p>
              <button class="flip-btn" aria-label="flip card">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-5.png" alt="Community" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MEET OLGA -->
  <section class="sp meet">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="meet-g">
        <div class="meet-v r"><div class="play"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#fff"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21"/></svg></div></div>
        <div class="r d1">
          <h2>Hi, I'm Olga.</h2>
          <p>For most of my 20s I was going through the motions — gaining weight, losing it, never really paying attention to what my body could actually do.</p>
          <p>That changed when I started training for real. I got stronger than I'd ever been. I trained through both pregnancies, stayed healthy, and never looked back. That was over 18 years ago.</p>
          <p>Since then I've coached thousands of women — in person at our gym and remotely through the app. The method works because I've lived it, tested it, and refined it with real people for nearly two decades.</p>
          <p class="creds">18+ years coaching experience · 7,500+ women coached · Strength & functional fitness specialist</p>
          <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-p">Start Training With Me <svg class="arr" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS / RESULTS -->
  <section class="testi sp" id="results">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="testi-h r">
        <h2>Results</h2>
        <p>What changes when you stop chasing punishment and start building strength.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-g">
        <div class="testi-c r">
          <p class="testi-q">"I finally feel strong again."</p>
          <p class="testi-s">The 30-minute workouts fit my life. The mindset work changed the way I approach food. For the first time, I'm not starting over every Monday.</p>
          <p class="testi-a">Michelle, 48</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testi-c r d1">
          <p class="testi-q">"Working out is my thing now."</p>
          <p class="testi-s">I never thought I'd say that at 52. This program made me feel capable again — not exhausted, not sore for days. Just strong and consistent.</p>
          <p class="testi-a">Janka, 52</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testi-c r d2">
          <p class="testi-q">"My back pain is gone."</p>
          <p class="testi-s">I came in wanting to lose weight. What I got was so much better — real strength, better energy, and I actually look forward to training now.</p>
          <p class="testi-a">Victoria, 45</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="sp" id="pricing">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="price-h r">
        <h2>Start Inside the App</h2>
        <p>7-day free trial. Cancel anytime. No pressure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="price-g">
        <div class="pc std r">
          <div class="pl">Monthly</div>
          <div class="pa">$19.99</div>
          <div class="pp">/month</div>
          <div class="pbo">&nbsp;</div>
          <ul class="pf">
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Daily follow-along workouts</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Nutrition guidance</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Mindset coaching</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Community access</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="pbtn">Start 7-Day Free Trial</button>
        </div>
        <div class="pc feat r d1">
          <div class="pb">Best Value</div>
          <div class="pl">Annual</div>
          <div class="pa">$199</div>
          <div class="pp">/year</div>
          <div class="pbo">2 months FREE</div>
          <ul class="pf">
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Everything in Monthly</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Save 2 months</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Priority support</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="pbtn">Start 7-Day Free Trial</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="fcta sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="r">
        <h2>Get stronger. Eat with awareness.<br>Keep going.</h2>
        <p>Start with a free trial. No commitment. Cancel anytime.</p>
        <div class="fcta-a">
          <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-p">Start Free Trial</a>
          <a href="/coaching" class="btn btn-g">Need more support? Explore coaching</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
